>งาน</span></h3>\n<p><wbr/><span>เริ่มต้น</span><wbr/><span>ใช้</span><wbr/><span>งาน</span><wbr/><span>ได้</span><wbr/><span>ง่าย</span><wbr/><span>ๆ</span> <wbr/><span>ใน</span><wbr/><span>ไม่</span><wbr/><span>กี่</span><wbr/><span>ขั้นตอน</span></p>\n<ol>\n<li><wbr/><span>เปิด</span><wbr/><span>กล่อง</span><wbr/><span>และ</span><wbr/><span>ดึง</span><wbr/><span>ผลิตภัณฑ์</span><wbr/><span>ออก</span><wbr/><span>มา</span><wbr/><span>อย่าง</span><wbr/><span>ระมัดระวัง</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>กด</span><wbr/><span>ปุ่ม</span><wbr/><span>เปิด</span><wbr/><span>เครื่อง</span><wbr/><span>ค้าง</span><wbr/><span>ไว้</span> 3 <wbr/><span>วินาที</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>เชื่อมต่อ</span><wbr/><span>กับ</span> Wi-Fi <wbr/><span>หรือ</span><wbr/><span>เครือข่าย</span><wbr/><span>มือถือ</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>เข้า</span><wbr/><span>สู่</span><wbr/><span>ระบบ</span><wbr/><span>ด้วย</span><wbr/><span>บัญชี</span><wbr/><span>ของ</span><wbr/><span>คุณ</span> <wbr/><span>หรือ</span><wbr/><span>สร้าง</span><wbr/><span>บัญชี</span><wbr/><span>ใหม่</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>ทำ</span><wbr/><span>ตาม</span><wbr/><span>คำ</span><wbr/><span>แนะนำ</span><wbr/><span>บน</span><wbr/><span>หน้า</span><wbr/><span>จอ</span><wbr/><span>เพื่อ</span><wbr/><span>ตั้ง</span><wbr/><span>ค่า</span><wbr/><span>เบื้องต้น</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>เลือก</span><wbr/><span>ธี</span><wbr/><span>ม</span><wbr/><span>และ</span><wbr/><span>ปรับแต่ง</span><wbr/><span>อินเทอร์</span><wbr/><span>เฟซ</span><wbr/><span>ตาม</span><wbr/><span>ความ</span><wbr/><span>ชอบ</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>ดาวน์โหลด</span><wbr/><span>แอป</span><wbr/><span>พ</span><wbr/><span>ลิ</span><wbr/><span>เค</span><wbr/><span>ชัน</span><wbr/><span>ที่</span><wbr/><span>คุณ</span><wbr/><span>ต้องการ</span><wbr/><span>ใช้</span><wbr/><span>งาน</span></li>\n<li><wbr/><span>เริ่ม</span><wbr/><span>ใช้</span><wbr/><span>งาน</span><wbr/><span>และ</span><wbr/><span>สนุก</span><wbr/><span>กับ</span><wbr/><span>ประสบ</span><wbr/><span>การณ์</span><wbr/><span>ใหม่</span>!</li>\n</ol>\n<h3><wbr/><span>ตาราง</span><wbr/><span>เปรียบ</span><wbr/><span>เทียบ</span><wbr/><span>รุ่น</span></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><wbr/><span>คุณสมบัติ</span></th>\n<th><wbr/><span>รุ่น</span><wbr/><span>พื้นฐาน</span></th>\n<th><wbr/><span>รุ่น</span><wbr/><span>กลาง</span></th>\n<th><wbr/><span>รุ่น</span><wbr/><span>พรีเมียม</span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><wbr/><span>หน่วย</span><wbr/><span>ความ</span><wbr/><span>จำ</span></td>\n<td>8 GB</td>\n<td>16 GB</td>\n<td>32 GB</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><wbr/><span>พื้นที่</span><wbr/><span>จัดเก็บ</span></td>\n<td>256 GB</td>\n<td>512 GB</td>\n<td>1 TB</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><wbr/><span>ราคา</span></td>\n<td>29,900 <wbr/><span>บาท</span></td>\n<td>39,900 <wbr/><span>บาท</span></td>\n<td>54,900 <wbr/><span>บาท</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><wbr/><span>การ</span><wbr/><span>รับประกัน</span></td>\n<td>1 <wbr/><span>ปี</span></td>\n<td>2 <wbr/><span>ปี</span></td>\n<td>3 <wbr/><span>ปี</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3><wbr/><span>ตัวอย่าง</span><wbr/><span>โค้ด</span></h3>\n<p><wbr/><span>สำหรับ</span><wbr/><span>นัก</span><wbr/><span>พัฒนา</span> <wbr/><span>เรา</span><wbr/><span>ได้</span><wbr/><span>เตรียม</span><abbr title=\"Application Programming Interface\">API</abbr><wbr/><span>ที่</span><wbr/><span>ใช้</span><wbr/><span>งาน</span><wbr/><span>ง่าย</span><wbr/><span>ไว้</span><wbr/><span>ให้</span><wbr/><span>แล้ว</span></p>\n<pre><code>// <wbr/><span>ตัวอย่าง</span><wbr/><span>การ</span><wbr/><span>เชื่อมต่อ</span><wbr/><span>กับ</span><wbr/><span>ระบบ</span>\r\nconst connection = await device.connect({\r\n    protocol: 'https',\r\n    timeout: 5000,\r\n    retries: 3\r\n});\r\n\r\nconsole.log('<wbr/><span>เชื่อมต่อ</span><wbr/><span>สำเร็จ</span>:', connection.status);</code></pre>\n<h3><wbr/><span>คำ</span><wbr/><span>ถาม</span><wbr/><span>ที่</span><wbr/><span>พบ</span><wbr/><span>บ่อย</span></h3>\n<h4>1. <wbr/><span>ผลิตภัณฑ